Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.31,0:00:03.60,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Tsurayuki! Ce naiba ai făcut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:04.93,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Îmi pare rău, bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:07.56,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Îmi era foame și nu era nimic altceva care să arate bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:10.32,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,How's that make it okay \Nto eat other people's stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:13.74,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Serios, chiar îmi pare rău!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:17.11,main,Roku,0,0,0,,De asta ți-am luat în schimb niște Sukiyamon! Vezi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:22.83,sign_409_7_Sukiyamon__Soy_F,Package sign,0,0,0,,Sukiyamon\N{\fs18\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H46488B&\bord4}cu sos de soia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.29,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,E cu sos de soia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.83,sign_409_7_Sukiyamon__Soy_F,Second Bag sign,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H363933&\3c&H62809A&}Umakatoyo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.13,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Umakatoyo is tonkotsu-flavored!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.83,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,They ain't the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:26.39,top,Roku,0,0,0,,I don't get the big deal. \NThey're both instant ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.97,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Starting this spring, \Nalong with enrolling in art school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:29.41,top,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,They can be the same kinda food, \Nbut that don't make them the same food!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:30.96,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,I've started living in this share house \Nwith some of my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:31.26,top,Roku,0,0,0,,In general terms, they're the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.25,top,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:36.59,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's two guys and two girls, which you think \Nwould be the ideal roommate setup, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:33.45,top,Roku,0,0,0,,They are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:34.56,top,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I want mine back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:35.57,top,Roku,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:38.60,main,Nana,0,0,0,,I heard the whole argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.97,main,Nana,0,0,0,,Tsurayuki, seriously, \Neating someone else's food
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.53,main,Nana,0,0,0,,is the one of the worst \Nthings a roommate can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:50.23,main,Nana,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why'd everyone go so quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:54.15,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Uh, well, Nanako... Your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.31,main,Nana,0,0,0,,My clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:04.89,main,Nana,0,0,0,,Quit looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.83,main,Nana,0,0,0,,I forgot I was in the middle of changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:09.88,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Hell of a puncher, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:14.33,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,For whatever reason, I ended up traveling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:16.88,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,ten years into the past \Nwith my memories intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:24.56,sign_1844_34_Do_not_eat_other,Sign,0,0,0,,{\frz13.6\move(185,265,205,255)\fax0.29\t(1,7680,\fs17)}Do not eat other people's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:19.60,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's what you might call a "time leap."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:22.61,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,My second attempt attempt \Nat college has so far been colored
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:24.56,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,with instant ramen's flavor and\Npainful hits to the solar plexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:27.44,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,along with hope and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.61,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,It won't be long before \Nwe start creating for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:35.03,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,I can't help but wonder what awaits us.
