Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:16.17,sign_54012_628_Sreenplay_Writin,Zoom out sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz0.58\pos(335,95)}Performance\N\NProduction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:16.17,main,Kano,0,0,0,,When it comes to filmmaking, \Nthese four areas are going to be crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:21.88,main,Kano,0,0,0,,I want you to form groups of four, \Nwith each person handling one area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.38,main,Kano,0,0,0,,The project is to be three minutes long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.11,main,Kano,0,0,0,,And I mean that seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:31.14,main,Kano,0,0,0,,because once you've all turned \Nin your shorts, we'll be screening them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.97,main,Nana,0,0,0,,Everyone's gonna see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.98,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Better make sure it turns out good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:40.90,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Finally, regarding the theme of the \Nshort films I want you all to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:46.73,main,Roku,0,0,0,,"Time" is kinda broad as far as themes go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.85,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,So broad it's hard to know \Nwhere to drill down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.27,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:53.80,main,Roku,0,0,0,,And there's a three-minute \Nlimit on our runtime, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.68,main,Roku,0,0,0,,That teacher isn't trying to make this easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.94,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's a good thing we were able to \Npick out our team so quickly, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:02.38,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Team Kitayama, featuring the roommates \Nfrom Share House Kitayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.44,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Kinda on the nose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.64,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're directing. Shinoaki's handling\N the technical side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.27,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Nanako's performing, and I'm production...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:15.61,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Well, I wanna do the script, but don't care \Nabout the performance side of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.15,main,Roku,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Kyoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.95,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd end up \Nat the same part time job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.25,main,Nana,0,0,0,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.16,main,Nana,0,0,0,,The manager gave me a funny look
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.35,main,Nana,0,0,0,,when he noticed we had the same \Naddress on our applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.67,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.88,main,Nana,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.37,main,Nana,0,0,0,,Here, hand that over. I'll put it on this shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.32,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Say, Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.75,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why'd you enroll in art school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.98,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Is there something you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.03,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,There wasn't any real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.11,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Maybe because I was sick of Lake Biwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.41,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,The big lake from where you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:03.17,main,Nana,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:08.38,main,Nana,0,0,0,,When I was in grade school, \NI used to think it was the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.77,main,Nana,0,0,0,,L-Listen, it's seriously huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.75,main,Nana,0,0,0,,You would've thought it was \Nthe ocean at that age, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.76,main,Nana,0,0,0,,Anyway, there's really nothing else to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.52,main,Nana,0,0,0,,I mean, there are towns and stores,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.80,main,Nana,0,0,0,,and you can find most things \Nyou need there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.53,main,Nana,0,0,0,,But I think if I had never left home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.77,main,Nana,0,0,0,,I would've never learned \Nwhat the ocean was really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:48.75,main,Nana,0,0,0,,The idea of time just passing by \Nin a place like that scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:53.04,main,Nana,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, here I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:58.19,main,Nana,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing to admit, but it's \Nkind of like I'm here to find myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:01.13,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I think I get what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.29,italics,Staff,0,0,0,,The doors are closing. Please stand clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:40.79,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Are you here for a similar reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.13,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.53,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.67,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.13,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,This goes up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.80,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Wait, Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.31,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Aw, it got caught on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.66,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Sorry, gimme one second...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.18,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.84,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Uh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:04.46,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Almost done...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.59,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,I might be trying to act like I did \Nwhen I was younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:12.46,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,but I'm still 28 mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.26,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Say, Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.61,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Uh... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:18.66,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,No sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.54,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's finish up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:26.04,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm sure I don't need to explain how \NI was in no hurry to finish up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.00,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Get those hands moving, Kyoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:40.73,sign_10963_109_Application,Sheet sign,0,0,0,,Application\N\N Team Name: {\fnComic Sans MS}Team Kitayama\N\N{\fnArial}Members\N{\fnArial}Direction: {\fnComic Sans MS}Tsurayuki Rokuonji\N{\fnArial}Production: {\fnComic Sans MS}Hashiba Kyoya\N{\fnArial}Technicals: {\fnComic Sans MS}Shino Aki\N{\fnArial}Performance: {\fnComic Sans MS}Nanako\N\N{\fnArial}Description:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.73,main,Kano,0,0,0,,You're going to fill this in, later, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.85,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Right. We're still not sure \Nwhat we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:48.12,main,Kano,0,0,0,,There's no telling when inspiration \Nwill strike, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.43,main,Kano,0,0,0,,Make sure to keep your antennae up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.48,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:55.81,main,Kano,0,0,0,,Has anything interesting happened \Nlately that you could use?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.37,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.92,main,Kano,0,0,0,,Well, it sure looks like something has.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.05,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,You have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.76,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Uh, no, nothing really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.83,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I-If you'll excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.63,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,We'd better figure this out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.97,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.19,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Shinoaki, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:34.71,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Can't eat another bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.05,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Come on. Time to finish eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:50.65,sign_12633_127_Important_Part,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Important\N Part
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:49.14,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kyoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.01,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,That was a real nice dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.24,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I had a bunch of Itoshima oysters to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.48,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:08.90,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Shinoaki, \Nwhy'd you enroll in art school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:14.42,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I can't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:17.68,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,so I wanted to find something I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.44,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,That's how I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.39,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's why you choose art school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.23,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:26.81,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I've never been real good at studying, \Neven in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.33,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I'd even miss the train a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.56,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,I can imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:36.47,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Since it was in the country, missing the\N train meant waiting for a whole half hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.97,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,The folks from the station \Neven got to know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.60,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.56,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I think I have an idea \Nthat goes with our theme!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.34,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of having the short \Ntake place at a train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.54,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Why a train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.15,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Since it's the type of place \Neveryone is familiar with,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:15.08,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,there's a lot of obvious shorthand \Nthat'll help people understand the setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:19.43,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,And I think it'd be well-suited to a story \Nthat wraps up in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.35,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,You've got a point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.06,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Everybody uses the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:36.11,sign_14942_150_Station,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(5739,1)\pos(150,175)}Station
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:27.45,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,And since stations tend to stay intact \Nfor long periods of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.61,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,they work well for depicting \Nthe passage of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.22,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,My idea is to use that to depict \Nthe life of one woman
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:36.11,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,over the course of three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:41.53,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,And I thought it might be good to have her \Nlife progress in tune with the time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.89,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.27,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting! I think it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.10,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I like it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.41,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see it screened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.22,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What do you think, Tsurayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.80,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Can I get a half-hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:58.95,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I wonder what that's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:10:59.93,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.46,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.44,main,Roku,0,0,0,,I wrote up a plot for the \Nsetup you described.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.40,main,Roku,0,0,0,,I figured it was what you were after.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.95,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Wow! This is exactly what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:20.30,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,You're really something, Tsurayuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.17,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,You were able to come up \Nwith something so quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.37,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,That's better than \NI figured you could manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:30.25,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't come up with the idea myself, \Nso I figured I should do this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.16,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,That settles it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.64,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,No objections!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:36.05,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm looking forward to the script—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.06,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Kyoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.23,main,Roku,0,0,0,,You got a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.60,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What is it, Tsurayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.39,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.63,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Something from my idea notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.29,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Isn't this—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.02,main,Roku,0,0,0,,It's the exact same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:05.32,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Your idea, and what I had \Nwritten down in my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.27,main,Roku,0,0,0,,I swear, I didn't see—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.18,top,Roku,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.58,main,Roku,0,0,0,,I actually had it locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.57,main,Roku,0,0,0,,You couldn't possibly have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:18.78,main,Roku,0,0,0,,But you still managed to come up \Nwith the same idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.75,main,Roku,0,0,0,,like you read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:25.21,main,Roku,0,0,0,,It honestly felt like you took \Nsomething right out of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:27.68,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Which is why I rushed \Nto write down the outline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.51,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:32.39,main,Roku,0,0,0,,It was scary, man, if I'm being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:39.36,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, how exactly \Ndid I come up with that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:43.49,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,I remember now... It was from \Na collection of short stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:48.48,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,A story about a woman's life, depicted against\N the background of a train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:54.29,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,I think the impression it left me with \Nis what had me imagine something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:59.67,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,And I didn't read that book \Nuntil some point in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:05.42,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Does that mean I essentially stole the idea \Nfrom Tsurayuki's future self?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.18,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Kyoya, is it just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:15.59,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Or is there something else going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.44,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Well, Kyoya? Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.37,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Yeah, it couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.46,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. \NIt has to be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.29,main,Roku,0,0,0,,It's not out of the question \Nfor different people to have the same idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.50,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,You've got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.43,main,Roku,0,0,0,,I've gotta be honest, I was kind of glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:46.71,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:48.27,main,Roku,0,0,0,,A train station makes for an easy setting,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.34,main,Roku,0,0,0,,both in terms of the possibility space \Nfor characters' behavior,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.92,main,Roku,0,0,0,,and the things that can happen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.90,main,Roku,0,0,0,,That's something that you pick up \Nfrom learning about screenwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:04.31,main,Roku,0,0,0,,But if anybody here at school \Nrealized that, I sure didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.90,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Which is why I was thinking about just \Ndoing the bare minimum for the project,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:10.28,main,Roku,0,0,0,,and focusing on my individual studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:15.58,main,Roku,0,0,0,,But I get the feeling we could make \Nsomething good together, Kyoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:19.83,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Let's give the teachers \Na real shock with our project!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:22.61,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.27,sign_20956_218_The_girl__,Text sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(905,1)\pos(421,92)}The girl_
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.60,main,Roku,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you want to make some cuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:08.05,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,As things stand, we're going to \Nend up going over three  minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.78,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,so I was hoping you could \Nrewrite the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:13.18,main,Roku,0,0,0,,I submitted the script we have \Nafter already rewriting it a bunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.34,main,Roku,0,0,0,,because I thought it was \Nthe best version of that story!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:19.48,main,Roku,0,0,0,,There's nothing in it \Nthat can be cut for time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.32,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:26.39,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Shinoaki, you can adjust the storyboards \Nto make sure everything fits, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.45,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.45,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,It should be doable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.84,main,Roku,0,0,0,,And if we pick up the pace with your lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.96,main,Roku,0,0,0,,we can cram them in within \Nthe time limit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.99,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Can we, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:40.26,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,I mean, I'd have to try...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.92,main,Roku,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.04,main,Roku,0,0,0,,We should at least try first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.14,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.75,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,There's a hard time limit \Non this assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:52.59,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,No matter how good the short turns out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.55,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,if we go past that limit, \Nwe'll be worse off for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:59.86,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,But is that good enough a reason \Nto convince Tsurayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.31,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Right now, this is probably \Nthe best I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:08.03,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's an assignment, after all, so we need \Nto follow the rules if we want the credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.13,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:14.36,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Okay. Fine. I'll make the cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.16,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tsurayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:21.62,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Is this your approach when it comes \Nto making something good, Kyoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.42,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Talk about lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:38.89,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Tsurayuki is such a perfectionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.98,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,If it's running long, we should \Njust make the cuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.67,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Don't let it bug you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:48.69,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,You there, the young lady stepping on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:54.96,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,I'm going to refrain from the impulse \Nto savor this sensation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:56.97,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,and ask for your help instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.20,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,If you have any sympathy for your senpai, \Nwho's run out of money from home,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.74,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,and is slowly starving to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:06.04,sign_24529_255_Fine_Art_Study_G,Sign,0,0,0,,Fine Art Study Group
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.04,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.54,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.17,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,This is a huge relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.86,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,It looks like I was able to make it back, \Nthanks to the three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.22,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,And now, freshmen—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.34,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,You're ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:22.89,main,Sugi,0,0,0,,Nice one, Prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:27.15,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,Looks like we can avert \Na third year of budget cuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.65,main,Kakihara,0,0,0,,We'll be able to survive another year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.94,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,I am seriously so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.63,main,Hiyama,0,0,0,,Sorry about the whole snare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.91,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal, so please, stop bowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.96,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,So, you're going to join the club, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.83,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,That is a different matter altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.83,main,Sugimoto,0,0,0,,It's no use after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.14,main,Kakihara,0,0,0,,Please! We're going to be \Nin real trouble without new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:48.61,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,Could we at least get permission \Nto use your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:49.68,main,Kiryu,0,0,0,,Please, Hashy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.84,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Please don't come up \Nwith weird nicknames for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.72,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I don't really have time \Nfor a circle, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:58.11,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about joining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.33,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too, as long as it's \Nfor a trial period.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.22,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.72,main,Art Club,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.58,main,Art Club,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:07.59,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.69,sign_26119_282_Fine_Art_Study_G,FLyer sign,0,0,0,,Fine Art Study Group\N\N{\c&HDEE3E0&\3c&H4248BF&\fs10}Now Recruiting Members
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:13.10,main,FLyer sign,0,0,0,,I'm Kiryu Takashi, in my fifth year \Nof the photography program.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.74,main,FLyer sign,0,0,0,,If you have any questions \Nabout taking pictures, I'm your man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.11,main,FLyer sign,0,0,0,,I'll make time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.88,sign_10963_109_Application,FLyer sign,0,0,0,,Location Release Form
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:38.81,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,Hashiba Kyoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.97,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Oh, chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.29,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Er, Kawasegawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:47.43,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,Is your team going to be filming \Nat the station, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.92,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Oh... yeah. Yours, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.26,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,You're not going to outdo us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.90,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,No matter what \Nyou're putting together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.70,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,my team intends to get \Nthe highest marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.36,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,O...kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:03.09,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,Don't think we're competing \Nat the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:05.09,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,Because we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.93,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,We're trying to make something good—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.08,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,Then let me ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.71,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,What's the concept of your short?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.21,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,What's the most important element of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.00,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,How are you going to use \Nthe three-minute runtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.80,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,You're handling production, \Nso you should have some idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.97,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.51,main,Eiko,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate filmmaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.07,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Here's the location release form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.94,main,Kano,0,0,0,,Have a seat, and I'll see about \Ngetting that stamped for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.85,main,Kano,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.86,main,Kano,0,0,0,,Sorry about—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:41.74,main,Kano,0,0,0,,Production's always got something \Nto worry about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:45.08,main,Kano,0,0,0,,I heard your group's got \Nsome creative differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:48.16,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Well, uh... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.49,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.46,main,Kano,0,0,0,,The script of a movie \Nthat came out the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.88,main,Kano,0,0,0,,It's had great reception, and seems likely \Nto win a few some awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.64,main,Kano,0,0,0,,But no one seems to like the actual movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:06.63,main,Kano,0,0,0,,The director and cast probably \Ndid whatever they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.80,main,Kano,0,0,0,,The runtime ended up too long, \Nruining the tempo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.85,main,Kano,0,0,0,,and wasting the strengths of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.44,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,This really is hard, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:15.01,main,Kano,0,0,0,,A script isn't a finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.45,main,Kano,0,0,0,,If the point was to just have \Npeople read something, and that's all,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.10,main,Kano,0,0,0,,it'd be better done as prose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:22.20,main,Kano,0,0,0,,At the script stage, \Nit can still go either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:27.76,main,Kano,0,0,0,,What you're doing isn't just \Na matter of subtraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.67,main,Kano,0,0,0,,If the production side stops trying, \Nthen that means the whole project is doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.96,main,Kano,0,0,0,,That's how important it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.67,flashback,Eiko,0,0,0,,You're handling production, \Nso you should have some idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.42,flashback,Eiko,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate filmmaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.80,main,Kano,0,0,0,,I've got one piece of advice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:46.80,main,Kano,0,0,0,,Everyone involved in the \Nfilmmaking process is a creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.18,main,Kano,0,0,0,,And no one outranks anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.52,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:02.16,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Whether it's ten years in the past \Nor the future, time is limited either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.68,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why didn't I realize that sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:11.14,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,I have to make sure I have no regrets, \Nor nothing will change at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.14,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tsurayuki! Tsurayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.13,main,Roku,0,0,0,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.13,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tsurayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.92,main,Roku,0,0,0,,What brought this on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.45,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,What? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.67,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:25.81,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I want to talk this over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.87,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,So please, can we make some time for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:32.18,main,Roku,0,0,0,,It's already decided. Just do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.81,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's not true! We haven't \Neven gotten started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.74,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're right, Tsurayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:39.86,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,We haven't filmed anything, \Nor started an edit yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.06,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,so it's too soon to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:43.80,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Kyoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.58,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,I want to talk this through as much \Nas we can, until the last minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.56,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,so we can decide what we can do \Nthat'll have the best result!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:52.40,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,We'll worry about time later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:57.62,main,Roku,0,0,0,,If you insist... I'm in, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.29,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.53,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Great weather today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:16.11,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,We picked a day where it was \Nsupposed to be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:17.44,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,There was planning involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:21.96,main,Roku,0,0,0,,It was hard work getting everything \Nto fit into three minutes too, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:22.94,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.79,main,Roku,0,0,0,,Let's make this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:25.66,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:28.95,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Oh... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:31.27,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.27,0:22:35.78,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,The camera that Tsurayuki-kun \Nborrowed isn't a video camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:38.13,main,Roku,0,0,0,,No, that can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:43.46,sign_10963_109_Application,Sign,0,0,0,,{\3c&H939490&\c&H1D2712&\fnComic Sans MS\fs25}O {\fnArial}Digital Single Lens Reflex Camera\N\h\h\h\hDigital Video Camera
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:43.48,main,Sign,0,0,0,,I marked the wrong one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:46.26,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Why not just go get the right one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.72,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,We can't. It'd take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:50.00,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.60,main,Roku,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I can't believe \Nit turned out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:55.87,main,Nanako,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone makes mistakes. \NNot much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.27,main,Shinoaki,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:02.45,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Is there... nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:14.78,sign_33157_376__If_there_s_no_c,Columsn; from right to left,0,0,0,,{\fad(799,1)}If there's no camera, then we can't film.\NIf there's no actors, we can't record a performance.\NIf there's no key art, we don't need to draw anything.\NIf the writer is missing, we shouldn't bother writing anything.\NIf there's not enough budget, we'll throw something together.\NIt is what it is. Nothing we can do about it.\NIt can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:06.57,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Didn't I spend my life ten years in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:09.55,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,repeating that excuse, \Nand regretting it every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:12.56,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,And now, when I've got \Nthe chance to do it all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.78,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Am I going to just do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:19.74,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Make excuses... and kick it all down the road, \Nwithout actually achieving anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:23.47,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,Put a hold on everything for ten years, \Nand see how that turns out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.30,italics,Kyo,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.80,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,We are not out of options!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:34.08,main,Kyo,0,0,0,,We're going to figure something out, damn it!
